sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Typography, Grid, Container, Box, Button } from '@mui/material'; import defaultPersonImage from '../assets/people/default.jpg'; import aishwaryaImg from '../assets/people/aishwarya.jpg'; import ramImg from '../assets/people/ram.png'; function People() { const currentMembers = [ { name: "Aishwarya Ganesan", role: "Assistant Professor", image: aishwaryaImg }, { name: "Ram Alagappan", role: "Assistant Professor", image: ramImg }, { name: "Xuhao Luo", role: "PhD student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Henry Zhu", role: "PhD student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Shreesha G Bhat", role: "PhD student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Jiyu Hu", role: "PhD student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Kiran Hombal", role: "PhD student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Chaitanya Bhandari", role: "MS student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Ramya Bygari", role: "MS student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Neil Kaushikkar", role: "undergrad thesis", image: defaultPersonImage } ]; const alumni = [ { name: "Wenqing Luo", role: "MS Thesis; First Employment: Apple", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Shubhi Jain", role: "MCS student", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Abhi Wangoo", role: "undergrad", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Akul Gupta", role: "undergrad", image: defaultPersonImage }, { name: "Amaan Khan", role: "undergrad", image: defaultPersonImage } ]; return ( People Faculty {currentMembers.slice(0, 2).map((person, index) => ( {person.name} {person.role} ))} Students {currentMembers.slice(2).map((person, index) => ( {person.name} {person.role} ))} ); } export default People;
